requestCodes.code:
client = LazopApiClient::Client.new(url, appkey, appSecret)
request = LazopApiClient::Request.new('/fbl/outbound_order_detail/get','GET')
request.add_api_parameter("outbound_order_no", "OO0120190614XXXX")
request.add_api_parameter("marketplace", "LAZADA_SG")
response = client.execute(request, accessToken)
puts response.success?
puts response.body

client = lazop.LazopClient(url, appkey ,appSecret)
request = lazop.LazopRequest('/fbl/outbound_order_detail/get','GET')
request.add_api_param('outbound_order_no', 'OO0120190614XXXX')
request.add_api_param('marketplace', 'LAZADA_SG')
response = client.execute(request, access_token)
print(response.type)
print(response.body)
